                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">1</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Efficiency of Use</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">A flight search takes​ numerous variables into account. The​
                                    “Recents” link allows users to quickly recall complex previous searches.</p>
                            </td>

                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">2</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Visibility of System Status</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Segmented controls make it difficult to identify current
                                    selection.
                                    Does black or white mean it’s selected?</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">3</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Understandable Interface Objects</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Icons in form fields quickly and accurately relay significance.​
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>

                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">4</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Error Prevention
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Users should not be able to select invalid starting points and
                                    destinations.​</p>

                            </td>
                        </tr>
