                <h3 class="pt-3">Selecting Specific Flights</h3>
                <p class="pb-3">Next, I reviewed the pages in the task flow where users chose departing and
                    returning flights.
                </p>
                <table class="table border-bottom mt-3">
                    <thead class="">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="narrow-th" scope="col"></th>
                            <th scope="col">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Heuristic</p>
                            </th>
                            <th scope="col">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Observation</p>
                            </th>

                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">1</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">User control and freedom</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Flight searches often have hundreds of results. Narrowing results
                                    to specific requirements expedites decision making.</p>
                            </td>

                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">2</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Recover from Errors / Flexibility</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">It’s easy for users to see if they chose the wrong date and
                                    identify which departure dates are cheapest.​</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <th scope="row">
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">3</p>
                            </th>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">Discoverability</p>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <p class="p-0 m-0">What is the difference between Flex and Latitude? Any attempt to
                                    hide complexity will serve to increase it.​
                                </p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
